The paper discusses unsupervised methods for generating training data for Question Answering, which falls under the sub-categories of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and named entity recognition (cs.NE), which are relevant sub-categories in the context of Question Answering.
